name: TechLife
0:
”Alexa, ask Tech Life what's going on today.”
”Alexa, ask Tech Life how the football team is doing.”
”Alexa, ask Tech Life when the next Spirit Day is.”
skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: tech life
des: Keep up with campus life at PCTVS! Just ask TechLife what's happening on a date and never miss another event. Or catch up with Bulldog Athletics and ask for the latest sports news, or scores for your favorite team. And if you're feeling low on wisdom, try asking what Spike has to say!
